<h2>Why Malaria, Why Now?</h2>
</div>
<div class="row">
  <div class="large-6 columns">
    <div class="paragraph" style="text-align:left;">
      <p>Malaria is responsible for more deaths than any other disease in  human history. We want to recruit you in the war against this debilitating and often fatal disease. Over the last 15 years an unprecedented global partnership has struck a massive blow for humankind, averting half a billion cases since the year 2000. However, the first cycle of this partnership is coming to an end in 2015, and more than ever we need the best minds engaged with the challenge of Malaria. Productive engagement can come in many forms- you can join one of the Malaria research labs on your campus. You can advocate for your governments increased contribution to Malaria efforts. And  you can contribute financially.</p>
